{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRETT
{DIALOGUE}: I'm Brett.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: I thought so.
{DIALOGUE}: Well, you remember your business partner Marsellus Wallace, dont'ya Brett?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRETT
{DIALOGUE}: I remember him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
