{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRETT
{DIALOGUE}: They're good.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: Mind if I try one of yours?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRETT
{DIALOGUE}: No.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: Yours is this one, right?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRETT
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jules grabs the burger and take a bite of it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: Uuummmm, that's a tasty burger.
