{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The spacious club is empty this time of day.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: English Dave crosses to the bar, and Vince follows.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: Where's the big man?
