{DIALOGUE}: Oh man, I'd give anything to catch 'em doin' it.
{DIALOGUE}: It'a been worth his doin' it, if I coulda just caught 'em, you know what I mean?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LANCE
{DIALOGUE}: It's chicken shit.
{DIALOGUE}: You don't fuck another man's vehicle.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSEUP – THE NEEDLE
