{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: You can have this one, cowgirl.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He hands her the rolled smoke.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She takes it, putting it to her lips.
