{DIALOGUE}: I'll do that.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. JACKRABBIT SLIM'S (LADIES ROOM) – NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mia powders her nose by doing a big line of coke off the bathroom sink.
