{DIALOGUE}: Who told you this?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: They.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mia and Vincent smile.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MIA
{DIALOGUE}: They talk a lot, don't they?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: They certainly do.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MIA
{DIALOGUE}: Well don't by shy Vincent, what exactly did they say?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Vincent is slow to answer.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MIA
{DIALOGUE}: Let me help you Bashful, did it involve the F-word?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: No.
{DIALOGUE}: They just said Rocky Horror gave you a foot massage.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MIA
{DIALOGUE}: And...?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: No and, that's it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MIA
{DIALOGUE}: You heard Marsellus threw Rocky Horror out of a four-story window because he massaged my feet?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MIA
{DIALOGUE}: And you believed that?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: At the time I was told, it seemed reasonable.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MIA
