{DIALOGUE}: But before he turns me into a bar soap, I'm gonna be forced to tell 'im about how you coulda saved her life, but instead you let her die on your front lawn.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. LANCE'S HOUSE – NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WE START in Lance's and Jody's bedroom.
