{CHARACTER_NAME}: JODY
{DIALOGUE}: Who's she?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lance looks up at Jody.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LANCE
{DIALOGUE}: Get that black box in the bedroom I have with the adrenaline shot.
