{DIALOGUE}: Get the fuckin' shot!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JODY
{DIALOGUE}: Don't yell and me!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She angrily turns and disappears into the bedroom looking for the shot.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WE MOVE into the room with the two men.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{META_DATA}: (to Lance)
{DIALOGUE}: You two are a match made in heaven.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LANCE
{DIALOGUE}: Look, just keep talkin' to her, okay?
