{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: What do you need a medical book for?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LANCE
{DIALOGUE}: To tell me how to do it.
{DIALOGUE}: I've never given an adrenaline shot before.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: You've had that thing for six years and you never used it?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LANCE
{DIALOGUE}: I never had to use it.
{DIALOGUE}: I don't go joypoppin' with bubble-gummers, all of my friends can handle their highs!
