{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mia is standing by the door.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She sees Vincent with English Dave.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: Mia.
{DIALOGUE}: How you doin'?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: MIA
{DIALOGUE}: Great.
{DIALOGUE}: I never thanked you for the dinner.
