{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His face looks like he went dunking for bees.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His TRAINER is on his knees, head on Floyd's chest, crying over the body.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The huge figure that is Marsellus Wallace stands at the table, hand on the Trainer's shoulder, lending emotional support.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We still do not see Marsellus clearly, only that he is big.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mia sits in a chair at the far end of the room.
