{CHARACTER_NAME}: ENGLISH DAVE
{DIALOGUE}: I'll take care of it.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. CAB (MOVING / RAINING) – NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Butch gets one of his boxing gloves off.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Esmeralda watches in the rearview mirror.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He tries to roll down one of the backseat windows, but can't find the roll bar.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUTCH
