{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Esmeralda can't keep quiet anymore.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ESMARELDA
{DIALOGUE}: Hey, mister?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BUTCH
{META_DATA}: (still working on the glove)
{DIALOGUE}: What?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ESMARELDA
