{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Everything seems normal.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: More or less the right number of cars in the street.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: None of the parked cars appear out of place.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: None of them have a couple of goons sitting inside.
