{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, I think so.
{DIALOGUE}: That means God came down from Heaven and stopped the bullets.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, man, that's what is means.
{DIALOGUE}: That's exactly what it means!
{DIALOGUE}: God came down from Heaven and stopped the bullets.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: I think we should be going now.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: Don't do that!
