{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: Jules, you ask me nice like that, no problem.
{DIALOGUE}: He's your friend, you handle him.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. JIMMIE'S KITCHEN – MORNING
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Three men are standing in Jimmie's kitchen, each with a mug of coffee.
