{DIALOGUE}: I'm the one who buys it, I know how fuckin' good it is.
{DIALOGUE}: When Bonnie goes shoppin;, she buys shit.
{DIALOGUE}: I buy the gourmet expensive stuff 'cause when I drink it, I wanna taste it.
{DIALOGUE}: But what's on my mind at this moment isn't the coffee in my kitchen, it's the dead nigger in my garage.
