{CHARACTER_NAME}: THE WOLF
{DIALOGUE}: – Winston, Jimmie – please, Winston.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JIMMIE
{DIALOGUE}: You gotta understand something, Winston.
{DIALOGUE}: I want to help you guys out and all, but that's my best linen.
{DIALOGUE}: It was a wedding present from my Uncle Conrad and Aunt Ginny, and they ain't with us anymore –
{CHARACTER_NAME}: THE WOLF
