{CHARACTER_NAME}: JIMMIE
{DIALOGUE}: Oak's nice.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. GARAGE – MORNING
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Both Jules and Vincent are inside the car cleaning it up.
