{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Both are twice as bloody as they were before.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: I will never forgive your ass for this shit.
{DIALOGUE}: This is some fucked-up repugnant shit!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: Did you ever hear the philosophy that once a man admits he's wrong, he's immediately forgiven for all wrong-doings?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JULES
{DIALOGUE}: Man, get outta my face with that shit!
{DIALOGUE}: The motherfucker who said that never had to pick up itty-bitty pieces of skull with his fingers on account of your dumb ass.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: VINCENT
{DIALOGUE}: I got a threshold, Jules.
{DIALOGUE}: I got a threshold for the abuse I'll take.
{DIALOGUE}: And you're crossin' it.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm a race car and you got me in the red.
{DIALOGUE}: Redline 7000, that's where you are.
