{DIALOGUE}: We're tradin'.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm washin' windows and you're pickin' up this nigger's skull.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. CHEVY NOVA – MORNING
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The interior of the car has been cleaned and lined with bedspreads and quilts.
