{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. COFFEE SHOP BATHROOM – MORNING
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Vincent, on the toilet, oblivious to the pandemonium outside, reads his "MODESTY BLAISE" book.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. COFFEE SHOP – MORNING
